Simple shooter for game built during a PyGame worshop

Homework:

Make our fighter able to attack the enemy
1. Add a button for shooting (inside the pygame.event.get_event loop)
2. Create a new sprite for FighterLaser
3. Create a new sprite group for FighterFire
4. Check for collisions between enemy ship and FighterFire
5. If there are collisions, deduct enemy energy and kill enemy if energy reaches 0


